# SAP MM Module

## Overview

This folder contains the Materials Management (MM) component of the SAP S/4HANA-inspired ERP implementation.

The MM module focuses on procurement, inventory management, vendor management, goods movements, and material planning to support hospitality operations and resource optimization.

## Scope

The implementation replicates selected SAP MM business processes using Python, SQLite, and Power BI.

Key areas include:

* Material Master Management
* Vendor Management
* Purchase Order Processing
* Inventory Management
* Goods Receipt and Goods Issue Processing
* Procurement Analytics

## SAP References

The project is inspired by the following SAP MM functionalities:

* Material Master Data
* Vendor Master Data
* Purchase Order Management
* Inventory Management
* Goods Movement Processing
* Procurement Reporting

